1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 8=

19
00:01:19,510 --> 00:01:21,509
Your Majesty, we've searched the area.

20
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:25,310
This place is under the heaviest guard.
Her Highness must be held inside.

21
00:01:25,950 --> 00:01:27,520
Surround the place.

22
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,360
Break in.

23
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,269
Yes, Your Majesty.

24
00:01:30,270 --> 00:01:31,060
Move.

25
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:01,500
- Let me go!
- Where do you think you're going?

26
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,800
Let go of me!

27
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:05,950
His Majesty won't spare you!

28
00:02:06,170 --> 00:02:07,270
Let me go!

29
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:10,800
He doesn't even know
how much longer he'll live.

30
00:02:10,990 --> 00:02:12,869
Since he's as good as dead,

31
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:14,390
why don't we...

32
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,590
Don't come near me!

33
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,160
Are you alright?

34
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:43,630
Your Majesty.

35
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,670
You finally came.

36
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:50,190
Don't be afraid.

37
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:54,310
You still owe me Qinghuan cakes.

38
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,670
With extra sugar.

39
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,310
Nan!

40
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:17,150
Fireworks!

41
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,349
They're beautiful.

42
00:03:18,350 --> 00:03:19,629
That's Bei's signal.

43
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:20,600
They did it.

44
00:03:22,670 --> 00:03:24,950
Do you like fireworks?

45
00:03:25,850 --> 00:03:26,740
Mm.

46
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:31,700
Let's watch them first.

47
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,229
Why are you here?

48
00:03:52,230 --> 00:03:53,390
My dear,

49
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,270
how do I look?

50
00:03:55,630 --> 00:03:56,550
You...

51
00:03:58,950 --> 00:04:00,520
You tricked me!

52
00:04:00,670 --> 00:04:01,990
If we didn't,

53
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,230
how would you take the bait?

54
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,870
He wants my throne,

55
00:04:05,970 --> 00:04:07,149
bullies my friend,

56
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,560
kidnaps my consort,

57
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,439
and now he wants to marry you.

58
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,040
I'm going to kill

59
00:04:12,550 --> 00:04:14,069
Sun Beiming.

60
00:04:14,070 --> 00:04:15,360
There's another way

61
00:04:15,550 --> 00:04:17,080
out of this.

62
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,960
You

63
00:04:19,110 --> 00:04:20,240
marry Sun Beiming.

64
00:04:20,670 --> 00:04:21,920
Gu Bei!

65
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:24,760
You actually tell me
to marry that traitor?

66
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:27,159
- Have you lost your mind?
- Gu Bei, Xiao Ling is my sister.

67
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,199
You only care about yours.

68
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,480
What about mine?

69
00:04:32,670 --> 00:04:34,199
Aren't we trying to think of a way?

70
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,549
What other choice do we have?

71
00:04:35,550 --> 00:04:37,290
Gu Nan is in their hands.

72
00:04:50,090 --> 00:04:54,110
How did you steppe people
get into the Princess's Residence?

73
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,679
Guards!

74
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,660
Guards!

75
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,999
Your men are already under our control.

76
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,150
You've lost.

77
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,730
Just admit defeat, my dear.

78
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,520
Watch out!

79
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,990
Gu Bei.

80
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,299
You're hiding behind

81
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:23,279
a woman?

82
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,990
How pathetic.

83
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:28,240
The world doesn't belong only to men.

84
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,339
Women can wear armor

85
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:31,510
and win glory too.

86
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,400
You lost because of your brains
and your skills,

87
00:05:34,550 --> 00:05:36,960
not because of your gender.

88
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:41,070
People laugh because I'm a woman.

89
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,319
They say if I were a man,

90
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,730
I'd be a great general.

91
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,560
Gu Bei.

92
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,500
You're the only one who understands me.

93
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,190
I may be a woman,

94
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,040
but I can still ride into battle.

95
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,360
I'm no less than any man.

96
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,800
If I die,

97
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:02,720
Gu Nan dies too.

98
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:05,299
Where is Gu Nan?

99
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:07,990
You'll never find her.

100
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,400
Everyone, stand down.

101
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:14,840
Then I'll leave her body intact.

102
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:16,610
In your dreams.

103
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,719
Impossible.

104
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,009
I hid her perfectly.

105
00:06:32,010 --> 00:06:33,599
How did you find her?

106
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,800
Sun Beiming,

107
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,920
I gave you a chance.

108
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:39,279
The moment you tried
to force Xiao Ling to marry you,

109
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,800
you had already lost.

110
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,189
The Imperial Guards have surrendered.

111
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:44,669
Surrender now,

112
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:46,800
and I'll leave your body intact.

113
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,039
I've prepared a special gift.

114
00:06:58,040 --> 00:07:00,960
It'll ensure everything goes smoothly.

115
00:07:13,190 --> 00:07:13,839
Protect them.

116
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,870
Nobody move!

117
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,310
Everything goes smoothly?

118
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:31,190
So this is what you meant.

119
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:44,510
Even if I've lost,

120
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:48,990
I'll drag all of you to hell with me.

121
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,759
Winner, winner,

122
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,750
chicken dinner.

123
00:08:06,370 --> 00:08:07,439
- Gu Bei!
- Your Majesty!

124
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,440
Your Majesty!

125
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:34,429
Nice one.

126
00:08:34,430 --> 00:08:36,309
I call it the Pocket Blaster.

127
00:08:36,310 --> 00:08:38,960
Good thing you caught my hint.

128
00:08:39,110 --> 00:08:40,039
When you said,

129
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:43,630
"Winner, winner, chicken dinner,"
I knew you were telling me you had a gun.

130
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,040
Your Majesty.

131
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,600
Thank goodness you're alright.

132
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,359
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

133
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,739
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

134
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:11,179
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

135
00:09:11,180 --> 00:09:15,559
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

136
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,969
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

137
00:09:17,970 --> 00:09:20,509
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

138
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:26,179
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

139
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:31,740
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

140
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:38,090
♪Funny moments never stop♪

141
00:09:38,710 --> 00:09:40,900
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

142
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:45,269
♪Yet through every up and down♪

143
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,240
♪We create miracles♪

144
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:50,000
♪From naive youths♪

145
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:52,739
♪To legendary heroes♪

146
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:54,689
♪This journey♪

147
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:58,699
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

148
00:09:58,700 --> 00:10:01,250
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

149
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:06,590
♪Let's create♪

150
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:16,550
♪A legend of our own♪

